				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">first go back to you home town I believe the person you seek is in the Tree house just up from the bank. Talk to her and hit all the key words then after that go to one of the camps and talk to one of the guys and say farstone to get you ADV stone. (The only one names I remember is in East commonland and is name Songbird i think). 
<br />

<br />
And the ADV stone lets you talke to magus to port from camp to camp and if placed on a charm (mainly your planner charm) will incress the stats of it. With the more ADV times 10 so ever 10 adv you pass in different areas the different stats go up. 
<br />
Exp: if you hunt in BB for the whole time you play EQ and pass 100 mission you will have some stats bonus of 10 in one stat like dex now move to North ro and do the same another stat like str is 10. Till you have all stats up to 10 that's AC, Dex, Str, AGI, STA, WIZ, INT, CHA, and resistes too and hp to 100 and mana to 100.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=656618" target="_blank" class="postlink">Veteran Yoagotindie Madmartgin</a> 
<br />
<a href="http://eqrangers.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">Level 64th Wood Elf Warder of Tunare</a> 
