			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Gonna clear up some misinformation.
<br />

<br />
For every 10 wins in a particular camp, your adventurer's stone will gain +2 hp/mana.  Once you have 50 wins in one camp, you also get +1 to all stats including saves.  Getting 100 wins in one camp will net you +2 to all stats/saves and +20 hp/mana.  Do that in each camp to get +10 to all stats/saves and +100 hp/mana.  Getting 9 wins in each of the 5 camps will get you nothing, you must have 10 in a single camp to get a charm boost.
<br />

<br />
Also, in order to trigger the stat increase you must hail a mob at the Wayfarer's camp.  You can do this every 2 wins and you will see "You have gained a valuable piece of information.".  He may also send you to hail another NPC to continue the process once you reach a certain number of wins.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=699885" target="_blank" class="postlink">Surefire</a>
<br />
Hunter of Fennin Ro</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
